Name: The Goracle
About the game: A classic RPG dungeon crawler. Play the role of a child, fresh off the turnip truck, called upon by fate to save the kingdom from the creature from the great abyss. Search out the Goracle for help in saving the kingdom. Complete quests, collect magic items, study the arcane arts, or learn a new (Kung) Fu.
